MQTT Server:
/etc/mosquitto/


Starting zigbee2mqtt: 
https://www.zigbee2mqtt.io/getting_started/running_zigbee2mqtt.html
cd /opt/zigbee2mqtt
npm start

view log: sudo journalctl -u zigbee2mqtt.service -f
